-- State Bank Mauritius Recommendation Raised to `Buy' at Axys Stockbroking
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2010-11-12T07:19:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-12/state-bank-mauritius-recommendation-raised-to-buy-at-axys-stockbroking.html
State Bank of Mauritius Ltd., the
Indian Ocean island nation’s second-biggest lender by market
value, had its recommendation raised to “buy” from
“accumulate” at Axys Stockbroking Ltd., the brokerage said in
an e-mailed statement from the capital, Port Louis, today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  